<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.11">
<l>naccuvār muṉṉiṟkum nārā yaṇaṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yaccō varukaveṉ ṟāycci yuraittaṉa</l>
<l>maccaṇi māṭap putuvaikkōṉ paṭṭaṉcol</l>
<l>niccalum pāṭuvār nīḷvicum pāḷvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who constantly sing the words</l>
<l>of the scholar-king of Putuvai with storied, ornamented mansions</l>
<l>that were spoken by the cowherdess, saying,</l>
<l>“Oh! Please come!”, to Nārāyaṇaṉ who stands before [His] devotees</l>
<l>will rule the high heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
